{"title_page": "Bali Ram Bhagat College", "text_new": "{{short description|degree college in Bihar}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date = March 2020}}\n{{Use Indian English|date = March 2020}}\n\n{{Infobox college\n| name           = Bali Ram Bhagat College, Samastipur  (Bihar)\n| native_name    = BRB College, Samastipur\n| image          =\n| location       = \n| address        = Mohanpur Road\n| city           = [[Samastipur]]\n| state          = [[Bihar]]\n| postalcode     = 848101\n| country        = [[India]]\n| affiliation    = [[Lalit Narayan Mithila University]]\n| founder        = [[Bali Ram Bhagat]]\n| principal      = Dr. L. P. Jaisawal\n| staff          = \n| teaching_staff = \n| established    = {{Start date and age|1969}}\n| gender         = \n| lower_age      = \n| upper_age      = \n| houses         = \n| type           = Government Co-Education Institute\n| system         = \n| enrolment      = \n| language       = \n| classrooms     = \n| campus         = Bali Ram Bhagat College, Samastipur  (Bihar)- 848101\n| Hours_in_Day   = \n| athletics      = \n| slogan         = \n| song           = \n| motto          = Impart Quality Based Education\n| nickname       = Bali Ram Yadav College\n| colours        = \n| founded        = \n| students       = \n| alumni         = \n| website        = {{URL|https://www.brbcollege.in/}}\n}}\n\n'''BRB College''' also known as '''Bali Ram Bhagat College''' is a degree college in [[Samastipur]] district of Indian state of [[bihar]]. it is a [[Constituent colleges]] of [[Lalit Narayan Mithila University]] <ref>{{cite web |title=constituent Colleges |url=https://lnmu.ac.in/constituent-colleges.php |website=Lalit narayan mithila university}}</ref> The college offers [[senior secondary education]] and [[undergraduate degrees]] in arts, science and vocational courses. The college was established in 1969 by [[Bali Ram Bhagat]] [[Yadav]].\n\n==Courses==\n* I.A. - Intermediate Arts\n* I.Sc. - Intermediate Science\n* B.A. - Bachelor of Arts\n* B.Sc. - Bachelor of Science\n* BCA - Bachelor in Computer Application\n* BBA - Bachelor in Business Administration\n\n== Campus==\nSri [[Karpoori Thakur]] ex-Chief Minister of Bihar helped in the lease settlement of land lying in an around the donated land with the District and State Administration.\n\n==Principal List==\n* Dr. Surendra Prasad\tPrincipal Incharge\t07-Aug-1969\t19-Apr-1975\n* Dr. Ramesh Yadav\tPrincipal\t01-Mar-2009\t08-May-2012\n* Dr. Surendra Prasad\tPrincipal Incharge\t01-Apr-1988\t17-Apr-1988\n* Dr. Krishnadeo Prasad Yadav\tPrincipal\t18-Apr-1988\t13-Sep-1997\n* Dr. Sitaram Singh\tPrincipal Incharge\t14-Sep-1997\t30-Nov-1997\n* Dr. Ram Narayan Rai\tPrincipal Incharge\t01-Dec-1997\t07-Apr-2002\n* Dr. Baleshwar Rai\tPrincipal Incharge\t08-Apr-2002\t16-Jan-2003\n* Dr. Chandrika Prasad\tPrincipal\t17-Jan-2003\t02-Feb-2003\n* Dr. Baleshwar Rai\tPrincipal Incharge\t04-Feb-2003\t10-May-2004\n* Prof. Wasiur Rahman Nomani\tPrincipal Incharge\t10-May-2004\t30-Sep-2005\n* Prof. Ram Narayan Rai\tPrincipal Incharge\t01-Oct-2005\t30-Nov-2005\n* Prof. Ram Narayan Singh\tPrincipal Incharge\t01-Dec-2005\t28-Jan-2007\n* Dr. Baleshwar Rai\tPrincipal Incharge\t30-Jan-2007\t28-Feb-2009\n* Dr. Awadhesh Kumar Singh\tPrincipal\t09-May-2012\t18-Aug-2012\n* Dr. Shambhu Kumar Yadav\tPrincipal\t19-Aug-2012\t30-Nov-2016\n* Dr. Ramesh Jha\tPrincipal Incharge\t01-Dec-2016\t10-Jan-2017\n* Dr. Meena Prasad\tPrincipal\t11-Jan-2017\t08-Feb-2017\n* Dr. K. K. Sahu\tPrincipal Incharge\t09-Feb-2017\t23-Jan-2017\n* Prof. Deepak Mehta\tPrincipal Incharge\t24-Apr-2017\t20-Aug-2017\n* Dr. L. P. Jaisawal\tPrincipal\t21-Aug-2017\t-[[Incumbent]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n{{official website|https://www.brbcollege.in/}}\n* https://lnmu.ac.in/constituent-colleges.php\n\n[[:Category:Universities and colleges in Bihar]]\n[[:Category:Lalit Narayan Mithila University]]\n[[:Category:1969 establishments in India]]\n[[:Category:Educational institutions established in 1969]]\n\n== Article Exte